{"tid":2387064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（玩鳩死黑警）一人一個忍辱負重既經驗","createTime":"2021-01-30T04:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T08:36:23.000Z","uid":42246,"like":82,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a22857caef81fbea841a59a0bf768cd217e055","tid":2387064,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:48:31.000Z","msg":"話說大半年前個中學黑警同學（以前叫做朋友）<br />\n問我可唔可以放低政見 試下做返朋友 <br />\n遲下做佢伴郎<br />\n咁大家都知疫情冇得擺酒啦<br />\n佢就話佢都係旅行結婚姐 唔擺酒<br />\n但想同母狗影輯婚紗相<br />\n想我有份做伴郎影<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我就話考慮下 過左成個月之後 佢再追問<br />\n咁我話ok啦<br />\n<br />\n到左11月個陣 <br />\n佢就約左某一日神咁早去d山卡拉地方影結婚相<br />\n咁我就話ok 到時我出埋車去啦<br />\n<br />\n咁結果當日 我當然係媳電話訓到自然醒<br />\n從此佢冇左搵過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都冇聽到有人睇過個輯婚紗相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5c83055bba32505d6f4f762a2449cbf391b10c","tid":2387064,"uid":27821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:51:00.000Z","msg":"Well done"},{"pid":"235114ff63501d3cbb7119d94c431ae321325eb5","tid":2387064,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304fcdb37416fca60a26e599194092a785e3f954","tid":2387064,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bea9ae44b6bfa7cab107ffd20779ed99001a2c","tid":2387064,"uid":321749,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"rep